5		Security & Resilience (Cross-Cutting)
		
		Rather than treating security as a separate chapter, ask these questions continuously across the system.
		
	1	Could a single key compromise stop operations?
	2	Can every critical component fail without downtime?
	3	Is every dependency monitored for vulnerabilities?
	4	Are secrets rotated automatically?
	5	Can I recover within minutes after a disaster?
	6	Are all critical events immutably logged?
	7	Can I replay any historical execution exactly?
	8	Are configuration changes versioned and reversible?
	9	Is every external dependency continuously health-checked?
		
